==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Embrave
<hw>Em*brave"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
inspire with bravery.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Beaumont.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To decorate; to make showy and fine.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And with sad cypress seemly it <qex>embraves</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Embrawn</ent>⟦br⟧
